'''訊息'''（{{lang-en|'''Messages'''}}）是一套在[[OS_X|masOS]]和[[iOS|iOS]]作業系統上運行的[[即時通訊|即時通訊]]軟體，由[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]開發。在[[iPhone|iPhone]]上同時具有[[簡訊|簡訊]]的功能。

訊息在2012年7月推出的[[OS_X_Mountain_Lion|OS X Mountain Lion]]上取代了原有的[[iChat|iChat]]即時通訊軟體。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/12/02/16/apple_unveils_mac_os_x_108_mountain_lion_coming_this_summer.html|title=Apple Unveils Mac OS X 10.8 Mountain Lion Coming this Summer|author=AppleInsider Staff|publisher=AppleInsider|date=February 16, 2012|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117155429/https://appleinsider.com/articles/12/02/16/apple_unveils_mac_os_x_108_mountain_lion_coming_this_summer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>除了保留大多數iChat的功能之外，訊息也加入了蘋果的即時通訊服務[[iMessage|iMessage]]和[[FaceTime|FaceTime]]整合。

==iOS版本==
===iPhone OS 3===
[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]在2009年6月推出的[[iPhone_OS_3|iPhone OS 3]]上將「訊息」設為內建預載的應用程式。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2009/06/16/iphone-30-guide/|title=iPhone OS 3.0 Released: What You Should Know|author=Ben Parr|date=June 16, 2009|publisher=Mashable|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312042659/http://mashable.com/2009/06/16/iphone-30-guide/|dead-url=no}}</ref>它取代了自初代[[iPhone|iPhone]]推出時既有的「簡訊」（Text）程式。其名稱的變更是由於iPhone在當時除了原有的[[簡訊|簡訊]]（SMS）外也開始支援[[多媒體短訊|多媒體短訊]]（MMS）。<ref name="iphone_os_3_0_press_release">{{cite press release|url=https://www.apple.com/pr/library/2009/03/17Apple-Previews-Developer-Beta-of-iPhone-OS-3-0.html|title=Apple Previews Developer Beta of iPhone OS 3.0|publisher=Apple Inc.|date=March 17, 2009|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202063835/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2009/03/17Apple-Previews-Developer-Beta-of-iPhone-OS-3-0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然第一代[[iPhone|iPhone]]、[[iPhone_3G|iPhone 3G]]和[[iPhone_3GS|iPhone 3GS]]都可升級至iPhone OS 3.0，但由於硬體限制，初代iPhone中的「訊息」程式並不支援多媒體短訊。<ref name="iphone_os_3_0_press_release"/>「訊息」也能夠使用vCard標準來分享聯絡人資訊。其他的重大變更包括支援複製與貼上，以及能同時刪除多則訊息的功能。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1139438/iphone30user.html|title=Cut and paste, MMS highlight iPhone 3.0 improvements|author=Peter Cohen|publisher=Macworld|date=March 17, 2009|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428105531/https://www.macworld.com/article/1139438/iphone30user.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===iOS 4===
「訊息」在2010年推出的[[iOS4|iPhone OS 4]]（隨後改名為[[iOS4|iOS 4]]）上有著小幅度的變更。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2010/04/08Apple-Previews-iPhone-OS-4.html|title=Apple Previews iPhone OS 4|publisher=Apple Inc.|date=April 8, 2010|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326131323/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2010/04/08Apple-Previews-iPhone-OS-4.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>新的功能包括可搜尋簡訊的文字內容，也加入了字數計算功能，能在輸入超過簡訊字數的上限時提醒使用者。iOS 4的「訊息」在簡訊發送失敗時會在圖示的右上方顯示一個內有驚嘆號的紅色圓形來提示使用者。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gizmodo.com/5568954/the-complete-guide-to-using-ios-4|title=The Complete Guide to Using iOS 4|author=Jason Chen, Rosa Golijan|date=June 20, 2010|publisher=Gizmodo|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317091242/http://gizmodo.com/5568954/the-complete-guide-to-using-ios-4|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ios_4_walkthrough">{{cite web|url=http://www.imore.com/ios-4-walkthrough|title=iOS 4 walkthrough|author=Rene Ritchie|publisher=iMore|date=Jun 14, 2010|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2014-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140731065108/http://www.imore.com/ios-4-walkthrough|dead-url=no}}</ref>蘋果也提供了新的[[應用程式介面|應用程式介面]]讓開發者能夠在自己的應用程式內加入傳送訊息的功能。<ref name="ios_4_walkthrough"/>

===iOS 5===
隨著2011年10月15日[[IOS_5|iOS 5.0]]的推出，[[iPad|iPad]]和[[iPod_touch|iPod touch]]也加入了「訊息」應用程式。<ref name="ios_6_press_release">{{cite press release|url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2011/06/06New-Version-of-iOS-Includes-Notification-Center-iMessage-Newsstand-Twitter-Integration-Among-200-New-Features.html|title=New Version of iOS Includes Notification Center, iMessage, Newsstand, Twitter Integration Among 200 New Features|publisher=Apple Inc.|date=June 6, 2011|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2013-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004213953/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2011/06/06New-Version-of-iOS-Includes-Notification-Center-iMessage-Newsstand-Twitter-Integration-Among-200-New-Features.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/apple-ios-5-release-guide-200-new-features-322508|title=Apple iOS 5 Release: A Guide to the 200 New Features|author=Dave Smith|publisher=International Business Times|date=October 10, 2011|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809181234/https://www.ibtimes.com/apple-ios-5-release-guide-200-new-features-322508|dead-url=no}}</ref>與iPhone同時支援簡訊、多媒體簡訊和[[iMessage|iMessage]]不同，iPad與iPod touch僅支援iMessage服務。iMessage可讓iOS 5的使用者透過[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]和[[3G|3G]]傳送文字訊息、圖片和聯絡人資料至其他的iOS 5裝置，且不需支付電信業者額外費用。此外，訊息在不同裝置間可以同步，使用者可於一台裝置上收發訊息後在另一台裝置上繼續。iOS 5的「訊息」在對方輸入文字時會同時提示使用者，也加入了「已傳送」和「已接收」的提示訊息。<ref name="ios_6_press_release"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-13579_3-20118920-37/apple-ios-5-review-modest-but-definitely-worthwhile/|title=Apple iOS 5 review: Modest, but definitely worthwhile|author=Jason Parker|publisher=[[CNET|CNET]]|date=October 12, 2011|accessdate=February 12, 2013}}</ref>新接收的簡訊、多媒體簡訊與iMessage訊息也能在鎖定畫面和[[通知中心|通知中心]]中顯示。

===iOS 6===
[[iOS_6|iOS 6]]強化了「訊息」應用程式在不同裝置間同步的功能。iPod touch和iPad的使用者可使用他們iPhone上的電話號碼來收發iMessage訊息（但無法傳送SMS和MMS）。 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2012/6/11/3078598/ios-6-unified-apple-id-phone-number|title=iOS 6 unifies your Apple ID and phone number for improved iMessage and Facetime support|author=Nathan Ingraham|publisher=The Verge|date=June 11, 2012|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506142714/http://www.theverge.com/2012/6/11/3078598/ios-6-unified-apple-id-phone-number|dead-url=no}}</ref>在此之前，iPhone使用者無法在iPod touch和iPad上接收傳送至iPhone電話號碼的iMessage訊息。此外，使用者可在任何iOS裝置上新增其他的電子郵件地址來收發訊息。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2013683/how-to-set-up-your-addresses-in-messages.html|title=How to set up your addresses in Messages|author=Glenn Fleishman|publisher=Macworld|date=November 9, 2012|accessdate=February 12, 2012|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312042017/http://www.macworld.com/article/2013683/how-to-set-up-your-addresses-in-messages.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>這些功能的設定都可以在「設定」應用程式中的「訊息」分類下找到。iOS 6也在如Safari和「照片」等應用程式中加入了分享按鈕，使用者能在不離開應用程式的情況下透過「訊息」來傳送網址和照片。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2010152/hands-on-with-ios-6-social-and-sharing.html|title=Hands on with iOS 6: Social and sharing|author=Lex Friedman|publisher=Macworld|date=September 20, 2012|accessdate=February 13, 2013|archive-date=2020-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200823212445/https://www.macworld.com/article/2010152/hands-on-with-ios-6-social-and-sharing.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==macOS版本==
===10.8 Mountain Lion===
在2012年2月16日，蘋果宣布「訊息」應用程式將以[[軟件版本週期#Beta|beta]]測試版的狀態加入[[Mac_OS_X_Lion|Mac OS X Lion]]（10.7）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2012/02/16/messages-beta-now-available/|title=Messages Beta now available for Mac OS X Lion|author=Tim Stevens|publisher=Engadget|date=February 16, 2012|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2018-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180910131633/https://www.engadget.com/2012/02/16/messages-beta-now-available/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外「訊息」也加入了[[OS_X_Mountain_Lion|OS X Mountain Lion]]（10.8）的開發者測試版中。Mac OS X Lion中的「訊息」beta版在2012年12月12日停止服務，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashgear.com/apple-officially-killing-messages-beta-for-lion-users-next-month-16257425/|title=Apple officially killing Messages beta for Lion users next month|author=Eric Abent|publisher=Slashgear|date=November 16, 2012|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117233118/http://www.slashgear.com/apple-officially-killing-messages-beta-for-lion-users-next-month-16257425/|archive-date=2013-01-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>時間剛好就在OS X Mountain Lion推出約三個月後。

正式版的OS X「訊息」應用程式在2012年7月25日推出，並包含在OS X Mountain Lion（10.8）中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2012/7/24/3184569/apple-os-x-mountain-lion-availability-july-25|title=Apple announces OS X Mountain Lion will be released on Wednesday|author=Chris Welch|publisher=The Verge|date=July 24, 2012|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2016-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160731160002/http://www.theverge.com/2012/7/24/3184569/apple-os-x-mountain-lion-availability-july-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>「訊息」取代了OS X中自[[Mac_OS_X_10.2|Mac OS X 10.2]]開始存在的內建[[即時通訊|即時通訊]]軟體[[iChat|iChat]]，加入了對[[iMessage|iMessage]]的支援。與iChat不同的是，新版的「訊息」不再支援[[AOL_Instant_Messenger|AIM]]、[[Google_Talk|Google Talk]]和[[XMPP|Jabber]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/apple/2012/07/os-x-10-8/8/#messages|title=OS X 10.8 Mountain Lion: the Ars Technica review|author=John Siracusa|publisher=Ars Technica|date=July 25, 2012|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130531014639/http://arstechnica.com/apple/2012/07/os-x-10-8/8/#messages|archive-date=2013-05-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>「訊息」也利用新加入的[[通知中心|通知中心]]來提示使用者新進的訊息。此外，在[[Safari|Safari]]、[[Finder|Finder]]和[[預覽程式|預覽程式]]等應用程式中新加入的「分享」按鈕，可讓使用者透過「訊息」來分享網頁、照片或檔案。「訊息」也支援使用拖曳的方式來分享檔案和照片。使用者也可在「訊息」內撥打[[FaceTime|FaceTime]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hongkiat.com/blog/mac-os-x-messages-features/|title=A Look Into: Messages – New IChat For Mac OS X Mountain Lion|author=Alvaris Falcon|publisher=Hongkiat|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312035835/http://www.hongkiat.com/blog/mac-os-x-messages-features/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在OS X 10.8.2的更新後，「訊息」新增了可用使用者的iPhone電話號碼來收發訊息。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tidbits.com/article/13275|title=Use Your iPhone’s Number with Messages in OS X 10.8.2|author=Glenn Fleishman|publisher=TidBITS|date=September 19, 2012|accessdate=February 12, 2013|archive-date=2017-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702035332/http://tidbits.com/article/13275|dead-url=no}}</ref>

